title: Visual Composer Popup Notifications v0.7 - wp Plugin
description:
Visual Composer Popup Notifications lets you add the popup notifications to your pages/posts. Notifications are shown on page load. You can customize the look of the popup by applying different themes and colors. Popups can be restricted to show only set number of times and can be hidden forever on close button click. Popups also support shortcode in the content so you can use any shortcode like gravity form shortcode to show form in popup or woocommerce product shortcode to show a certain product etc.

Note : You need Visual Composer installed before you can use this addon.

Product page: http://codecanyon.net/item/visual-composer-popup-notifications/8215036

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
